title: DKS Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of Dick's Sporting Goods, Inc (Symbol: DKS) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $35.65, changing hands as high as $36.13 per share.
